title: 4 friends killed in car crash on their way to Devi Patan Temple
title_detail: {'type': 'text/plain', 'language': 'en-IN', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeeds/-2128819658.cms', 'value': '4 friends killed in car crash on their way to Devi Patan Temple'}
summary: Four friends lost their lives in a car accident after their SUV crashed into a tree near Benduli village in Gonda. They were en route to Balrampur Devipatan Temple during Navratri.
